---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '../../../components/ui/Card';
import { CodeBlock } from '../../../components/ui/CodeBlock';
---

<BaseLayout title="Understanding SuperInstance - SuperInstance.AI Documentation">
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="animate-fade-in">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <a href="/docs" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
            </svg>
            Back to Documentation
          </a>
        </div>

        <h1 class="heading-1 mb-6">
          Understanding SuperInstance: The Universal Cell Architecture
        </h1>

        <p class="text-body max-w-3xl mb-10">
          SuperInstance revolutionizes spreadsheet AI by treating every cell as a universal instance—
          any data type, any computation, any AI model—all within a single cell. Learn how this
          breakthrough architecture transforms how we think about spreadsheets.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-lg px-4 py-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary-700">Reading time: 10 minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-accent-50 rounded-lg px-4 py-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-700">Level: Intermediate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-secondary-50 rounded-lg px-4 py-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-secondary-700">Prerequisites: Basic spreadsheet knowledge</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-16">

        <!-- Core Concept -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6">The Core Concept: Every Cell = Any Instance</h2>

          <p class="text-body mb-6">
            Traditional spreadsheets force you to choose: is cell A1 a number, text, or formula?
            SuperInstance eliminates this limitation with universal cell architecture.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-primary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-500 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">Key Insight</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-primary-800">
              A SuperInstance cell can simultaneously be: a data repository, an AI model processor,
              a geometric calculator, and a pattern detector—all without changing the cell type.
            </p>
          </div>

          <Card hover className="mb-6">
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>Traditional Limitation</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              <CodeBlock code={`// Excel: Different cell types for different purposes
A1: =SUM(B1:B10)        // Formula cell
A2: "Customer Name"     // Text cell
A3: 42                  // Number cell
A4: 0.15                // Percentage cell

// Each cell has ONE fixed type
// Changing type requires manual intervention`} lang="javascript" />
            </CardContent>
          </Card>

          <Card hover>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>SuperInstance Solution</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              <CodeBlock code={`// SuperInstance: Universal cell architecture
A1: =SuperInstance("detect the pattern in column B and predict next values")
A1: =SuperInstance("convert this text to numerical sentiment score")
A1: =SuperInstance("apply geometric transformation to these coordinates")

// Same cell, different computations based on content and context`} lang="javascript" />
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <!-- How It Works -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6">How SuperInstance Works</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>1. Content Analysis</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  The cell analyzes surrounding data, formulas, and patterns to understand context.
                </p>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>2. Type Inference</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Based on content, it infers the most appropriate computation type.
                </p>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>3. Dynamic Execution</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  Executes the appropriate computation without being explicitly told.
                </p>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </div>

          <h3 class="heading-3 mb-4">Example: Smart Data Detection</h3>
          <p class="text-body mb-4">
            Watch how SuperInstance adapts to different inputs in the same cell:
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm">
              <div class="text-green-400">// Input: Financial data</div>
              <div>A1: "Sales: $12,500 (15% growth)"</div>
              <div class="text-blue-400 mt-2">// SuperInstance response:</div>
              <div>=SIParse("12,500", currency) * 1.15</div>
              <div class="text-green-400 mt-2">// Output: $14,375 (calculated)</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm">
              <div class="text-green-400">// Input: Date string</div>
              <div>A1: "Meeting scheduled for next Tuesday"</div>
              <div class="text-blue-400 mt-2">// SuperInstance response:</div>
              <div>=ConvertToDate("next Tuesday", TODAY())</div>
              <div class="text-green-400 mt-2">// Output: 2024-01-16 (actual date)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Confidence Cascade System -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6">The Confidence Cascade: Intelligent Activation</h2>

          <p class="text-body mb-6">
            Not all computations should run immediately. SuperInstance uses a confidence cascade
            to determine when to activate, similar to how neurons in the brain don't fire for
            every stimulus.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-accent-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-accent-900 mb-3">Confidence Zones</h3>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-green-500 rounded mr-3"></div>
                <span><strong>High Confidence (>80%):</strong> Immediate execution</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-500 rounded mr-3"></div>
                <span><strong>Medium Confidence (40-80%):</strong> Flag for review</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-red-500 rounded mr-3"></div>
                <span><strong>Low Confidence (<40%):</strong> Wait for more data</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <CodeBlock code={`// Example: Sales prediction with confidence
A1: "Q1 sales down 5%, Q2 flat, Q3 up 12%"

// SuperInstance analysis:
Confidence Model: 0.85
Pattern Match:    0.92  (Seasonal pattern found)
Data Quality:     0.79  (Three data points)
Overall:          0.85  (HIGH - Execute immediately)

Result: "Q4 predicted: +8% based on historical pattern"

// Low confidence example:
A2: "Sales varied"
// Too vague - waits for more specific data`} lang="javascript" />
        </div>

        <!-- Practical Applications -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6">Practical Applications</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>Financial Analysis</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                  Mix data types naturally:
                </p>
                <CodeBlock code={`A1: "Revenue: $2.5M (↓12%)"
// SuperInstance detects currency, percentage,
// and trend direction automatically`} lang="javascript" />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>Scientific Data</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                  Process complex measurements:
                </p>
                <CodeBlock code={`B1: "Temp: 98.6°F (37°C) ±0.5°"
// SuperInstance handles unit conversions,
// ranges, and uncertainty`} lang="javascript" />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>Natural Language Queries</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                  Ask questions in plain English:
                </p>
                <CodeBlock code={`C1: "What's the average of column B?"
// SuperInstance converts to:
=AVERAGE(B:B)`} lang="javascript" />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <Card hover>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>Pattern Recognition</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                  Discover hidden patterns:
                </p>
                <CodeBlock code={`D1: "Data seems seasonal"
// SuperInstance analyzes time series,
// identifies periodic patterns`} lang="javascript" />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Getting Started -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6">Getting Started with SuperInstance</h2>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-accent-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Try SuperInstance?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
              Start with these simple experiments to experience universal cell architecture:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8 text-lg">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Mix text and numbers: "Total: 42 items"
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Ask natural questions: "Sum of Q1"
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Include context: "Revenue ↓10% from last year"
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/docs/tutorials/first-automation" class="bg-white text-primary-600 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-block">
              Try Your First SuperInstance
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Next Steps -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6">Next Steps</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <a href="/docs/concepts/confidence-cascade" class="bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Confidence Cascade</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Learn how SuperInstance's confidence system works</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/docs/concepts/polln-notation" class="bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">POLLN Notation</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Understand the mathematical foundation</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/docs/tutorials/advanced-patterns" class="bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advanced Patterns</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Explore complex data patterns and automation</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>